1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: ww.h,v 1.8 2002/06/12 06:07:17 mpech Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: ww.h,v 1.9 1996/10/12 23:46:23 christos Exp $	*/

/*
